{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/az-bulunurluk/","webpackCompilationHash":"0743168de7141a7dc4bc","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"author":"Burak Tokak","description":"SaaS, e-ticaret ve diğer dijital ürünlerinizin verimini arttırmak için kullanabileceğiniz ücretsiz ve örneklerle destekli bir psikolojik prensip kütüphanesidir.","facebookAppId":"310591556081648","title":"Dijital Psikoloji","twitterHandle":"danistefanovic","siteUrl":"https://dijitalpsikoloji.com"}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Bir şeye sahip olmamız ne kadar zorsa, onu o derece fazla isteriz. İnsanlar genelde bir şeyin mevcut olma veya erişilebilmesi durumunu bu şeyin kalitesine bağlarlar. <a href=\"/kayip-kahri/\">Kayıp kahrı</a> konseptinde görülebileceği gibi; bir şeyi kaybetme korkusu, bu şeyi elde etme isteğinden daha fazla motive edicidir.</p>\n<h2>Studies</h2>\n<p>Women are more attracted to men who are in a relationship than to single guys (<a href=\"http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0022103109001048?via=ihub\">Parker &#x26; Burkley, 2009</a>). It seems when something is limited or unattainable, it becomes more attractive.</p>\n<p>One study by <a href=\"http://psycnet.apa.org/record/1976-03817-001\">Worchel, Lee and Adewole (1975)</a> showed that people value cookies more highly if they’re scarce. Some participants were given a glass jar with ten cookies, while others only received two. In another condition, where the number of cookies was reduced from ten to two, participants rated these cookies the highest.</p>\n<p>Scarcity tactics tend to be more effective when targeted at customers who have a greater than average need for uniqueness (<a href=\"http://scholarship.sha.cornell.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1181&#x26;context=articles\">Lynn, 1991</a>).</p>\n<h2>Examples</h2>\n<h3>Limited stock</h3>\n<p>Almost every e-commerce website employs scarcity by showing how few items are available in stock. As shown above in the cookie experiment by Worchel et al., we value those things more that have recently become less available to us.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 550px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Scarcity Example: Limited stock\"\n        title=\"Scarcity Example: Limited stock\"\n        src=\"/static/58c026bdf76a8570b01fb76c38831c4f/2cf63/01-quantity-countdown.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/58c026bdf76a8570b01fb76c38831c4f/2456f/01-quantity-countdown.png 138w,\n/static/58c026bdf76a8570b01fb76c38831c4f/90c99/01-quantity-countdown.png 275w,\n/static/58c026bdf76a8570b01fb76c38831c4f/2cf63/01-quantity-countdown.png 550w,\n/static/58c026bdf76a8570b01fb76c38831c4f/8cead/01-quantity-countdown.png 825w,\n/static/58c026bdf76a8570b01fb76c38831c4f/566ce/01-quantity-countdown.png 1100w,\n/static/58c026bdf76a8570b01fb76c38831c4f/6ff5e/01-quantity-countdown.png 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Limited stock for a particular model or size</h3>\n<p>Go even further and show how many items are available for a specific type, color or size or a combination of them.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 550px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Scarcity Example: Limited stock for a particular model or size\"\n        title=\"Scarcity Example: Limited stock for a particular model or size\"\n        src=\"/static/1270a22c59f8752d88768e58eeea35b4/2cf63/02-limited-stock-model.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1270a22c59f8752d88768e58eeea35b4/2456f/02-limited-stock-model.png 138w,\n/static/1270a22c59f8752d88768e58eeea35b4/90c99/02-limited-stock-model.png 275w,\n/static/1270a22c59f8752d88768e58eeea35b4/2cf63/02-limited-stock-model.png 550w,\n/static/1270a22c59f8752d88768e58eeea35b4/8cead/02-limited-stock-model.png 825w,\n/static/1270a22c59f8752d88768e58eeea35b4/566ce/02-limited-stock-model.png 1100w,\n/static/1270a22c59f8752d88768e58eeea35b4/6ff5e/02-limited-stock-model.png 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Exposing people to other buyers</h3>\n<p>While you’re looking around and considering whether or not to book this hotel room, you suddenly realize that another person is checking out the same property. The fear of loss kicks in. Indicating how many people are currently viewing the same item is a powerful tactic to play up the scarcity game.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 550px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Scarcity Example: Exposing people to other buyers\"\n        title=\"Scarcity Example: Exposing people to other buyers\"\n        src=\"/static/2b9ab27efa61754120e1f4f7264f2878/2cf63/03-real-time-user-count.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2b9ab27efa61754120e1f4f7264f2878/2456f/03-real-time-user-count.png 138w,\n/static/2b9ab27efa61754120e1f4f7264f2878/90c99/03-real-time-user-count.png 275w,\n/static/2b9ab27efa61754120e1f4f7264f2878/2cf63/03-real-time-user-count.png 550w,\n/static/2b9ab27efa61754120e1f4f7264f2878/8cead/03-real-time-user-count.png 825w,\n/static/2b9ab27efa61754120e1f4f7264f2878/566ce/03-real-time-user-count.png 1100w,\n/static/2b9ab27efa61754120e1f4f7264f2878/6ff5e/03-real-time-user-count.png 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Deadlines</h3>\n<p>Give your prospects a reason to act now by exposing them to time limits. But, be careful. Unfortunately, some businesses started using this technique in scammy ways, which may lead people to consider your offer more carefully.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 550px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Scarcity Example: Deadlines\"\n        title=\"Scarcity Example: Deadlines\"\n        src=\"/static/2891c79798e22e8149bfc400438f348d/2cf63/04-deadlines.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2891c79798e22e8149bfc400438f348d/2456f/04-deadlines.png 138w,\n/static/2891c79798e22e8149bfc400438f348d/90c99/04-deadlines.png 275w,\n/static/2891c79798e22e8149bfc400438f348d/2cf63/04-deadlines.png 550w,\n/static/2891c79798e22e8149bfc400438f348d/8cead/04-deadlines.png 825w,\n/static/2891c79798e22e8149bfc400438f348d/566ce/04-deadlines.png 1100w,\n/static/2891c79798e22e8149bfc400438f348d/6ff5e/04-deadlines.png 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Limited time offers with countdown timers</h3>\n<p>Use animated timers to draw even more on people’s fear of missing out. This tactic is often used with some perceived benefit for acting fast, like a reduced price or some additional bonus items.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 550px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Scarcity Example: Limited time offers with countdown timers\"\n        title=\"Scarcity Example: Limited time offers with countdown timers\"\n        src=\"/static/66f803108e1b51ddcf92459e293487f3/2cf63/05-limited-time-countdown.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/66f803108e1b51ddcf92459e293487f3/2456f/05-limited-time-countdown.png 138w,\n/static/66f803108e1b51ddcf92459e293487f3/90c99/05-limited-time-countdown.png 275w,\n/static/66f803108e1b51ddcf92459e293487f3/2cf63/05-limited-time-countdown.png 550w,\n/static/66f803108e1b51ddcf92459e293487f3/8cead/05-limited-time-countdown.png 825w,\n/static/66f803108e1b51ddcf92459e293487f3/566ce/05-limited-time-countdown.png 1100w,\n/static/66f803108e1b51ddcf92459e293487f3/6ff5e/05-limited-time-countdown.png 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Time constraints for next-day shipping</h3>\n<p>Amazon shows the exact remaining time within which the purchase has to be completed to qualify for next-day shipping. Shoppers who need a product immediately will impulsively buy it to ensure that they get it the next day.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 550px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Scarcity Example: Time constraints for next-day shipping\"\n        title=\"Scarcity Example: Time constraints for next-day shipping\"\n        src=\"/static/256a5c0e6a017c68b5cbb6f21165c087/2cf63/06-next-day-shipping.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/256a5c0e6a017c68b5cbb6f21165c087/2456f/06-next-day-shipping.png 138w,\n/static/256a5c0e6a017c68b5cbb6f21165c087/90c99/06-next-day-shipping.png 275w,\n/static/256a5c0e6a017c68b5cbb6f21165c087/2cf63/06-next-day-shipping.png 550w,\n/static/256a5c0e6a017c68b5cbb6f21165c087/8cead/06-next-day-shipping.png 825w,\n/static/256a5c0e6a017c68b5cbb6f21165c087/566ce/06-next-day-shipping.png 1100w,\n/static/256a5c0e6a017c68b5cbb6f21165c087/6ff5e/06-next-day-shipping.png 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Reducing the free trial length</h3>\n<p>When Hiten Shah, the co-founder of KISSmetrics, decreased the length of the trial period from 30 to 14 days, he saw a <a href=\"https://www.quicksprout.com/2013/01/14/11-obvious-ab-tests-you-should-try/\">102% increase in the usage</a> of the product. The reduction made people feel that they had to use the service as soon as possible.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 550px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Scarcity Example: Reducing the free trial length\"\n        title=\"Scarcity Example: Reducing the free trial length\"\n        src=\"/static/8072b26e165903c379ea2d3993467dc6/2cf63/07-reducing-trial-period.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8072b26e165903c379ea2d3993467dc6/2456f/07-reducing-trial-period.png 138w,\n/static/8072b26e165903c379ea2d3993467dc6/90c99/07-reducing-trial-period.png 275w,\n/static/8072b26e165903c379ea2d3993467dc6/2cf63/07-reducing-trial-period.png 550w,\n/static/8072b26e165903c379ea2d3993467dc6/8cead/07-reducing-trial-period.png 825w,\n/static/8072b26e165903c379ea2d3993467dc6/566ce/07-reducing-trial-period.png 1100w,\n/static/8072b26e165903c379ea2d3993467dc6/6ff5e/07-reducing-trial-period.png 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Online auctions</h3>\n<p>A single-unit auction combines several scarcity elements at the same time: it’s limited by quantity and time. Multiple people bid on one item in a limited timeframe, and there can be only one winner – a mix which led eBay to become such a huge company.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 550px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Scarcity Example: Online auctions\"\n        title=\"Scarcity Example: Online auctions\"\n        src=\"/static/427e384b532b9825e3a0d5ae35a097a9/2cf63/08-online-auctions.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/427e384b532b9825e3a0d5ae35a097a9/2456f/08-online-auctions.png 138w,\n/static/427e384b532b9825e3a0d5ae35a097a9/90c99/08-online-auctions.png 275w,\n/static/427e384b532b9825e3a0d5ae35a097a9/2cf63/08-online-auctions.png 550w,\n/static/427e384b532b9825e3a0d5ae35a097a9/8cead/08-online-auctions.png 825w,\n/static/427e384b532b9825e3a0d5ae35a097a9/566ce/08-online-auctions.png 1100w,\n/static/427e384b532b9825e3a0d5ae35a097a9/6ff5e/08-online-auctions.png 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3>Restricting features and content availability</h3>\n<p>In today’s online world, everything seems to be permanently available in abundance. Snapchat has reintroduced scarcity into the entertainment sector. If you miss a story on Snapchat, which is only available for 24 hours, you will never see it again. This feature is definitely one part of the app that makes it so sticky, and persuades users to come back. Is there something in your product that can be made artificially scarce?</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 550px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.333333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Scarcity Example: Restricting features and content availability\"\n        title=\"Scarcity Example: Restricting features and content availability\"\n        src=\"/static/f44f5594e542fc14c30e00d72cd26ccd/2cf63/09-limiting-feature-availability.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f44f5594e542fc14c30e00d72cd26ccd/2456f/09-limiting-feature-availability.png 138w,\n/static/f44f5594e542fc14c30e00d72cd26ccd/90c99/09-limiting-feature-availability.png 275w,\n/static/f44f5594e542fc14c30e00d72cd26ccd/2cf63/09-limiting-feature-availability.png 550w,\n/static/f44f5594e542fc14c30e00d72cd26ccd/8cead/09-limiting-feature-availability.png 825w,\n/static/f44f5594e542fc14c30e00d72cd26ccd/566ce/09-limiting-feature-availability.png 1100w,\n/static/f44f5594e542fc14c30e00d72cd26ccd/6ff5e/09-limiting-feature-availability.png 1200w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>","fields":{"path":"/az-bulunurluk/","slug":"az-bulunurluk"},"frontmatter":{"datePublished":"2017-09-11T08:15:15Z","title":"Az Bulunurluk","seoImage":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/9fb6f241773b0d1de5d7c4c2bce6f409/fef60/seo-image.png"}}}}},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"fields":{"path":"/adanma-sureklilik/","slug":"adanma-sureklilik"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Adanma ve Süreklilik"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"path":"/az-bulunurluk/","slug":"az-bulunurluk"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Az Bulunurluk"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"path":"/capalanmislik/","slug":"capalanmislik"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Çapalanmışlık"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"path":"/kayip-kahri/","slug":"kayip-kahri"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Kayıp Kahrı"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"path":"/mutekabiliyet/","slug":"mutekabiliyet"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Mütekabiliyet"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"path":"/odullendirme/","slug":"odullendirme"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Ödüllendirme"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"path":"/sosyal-dayanak/","slug":"sosyal-dayanak"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Sosyal Dayanak"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"path":"/tamamlama-ihtiyaci/","slug":"tamamlama-ihtiyaci"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Tamamlama İhtiyacı"}}},{"node":{"fields":{"path":"/tetikleyiciler/","slug":"tetikleyiciler"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Tetikleyiciler"}}}]}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"az-bulunurluk"}}}